title: Rashod Bateman with PA #92Noon!
description: Rashod Bateman was nearly an instant star for Gophers football, but chose to opt out of the 2020 season(which has since been canceled) because of the pandemic. Bateman and his agent, Blake Baratz, sat down with PA for a couple segments!
